---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Blog — Rupadana">
  <section class="hero reveal">
    <h1>Notes on systems, tools, and useful software.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      A small place for technical writing, ideas, and practical notes on building products,
      backend systems, and developer workflows.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="article-list reveal">
    <article class="card">
      <span class="tag">Tools</span>
      <h2>code-server: VS Code in the Browser</h2>
      <p>
        Run VS Code on any remote server and access it from any device with a web browser.
      </p>
      <a class="inline-link" href="/blog/code-server-vscode-in-the-browser">Read article →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <span class="tag">No-Code</span>
      <h2>NocoDB: Open-Source Airtable Alternative</h2>
      <p>
        Turn any SQL database into a smart spreadsheet with full collaboration features and instant APIs.
      </p>
      <a class="inline-link" href="/blog/nocodb-open-source-airtable-alternative">Read article →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <span class="tag">Data</span>
      <h2>Metabase: Business Intelligence Made Easy</h2>
      <p>
        Make data-driven decisions without needing to be an SQL expert. An introduction to the most popular open-source BI tool.
      </p>
      <a class="inline-link" href="/blog/metabase-business-intelligence-made-easy">Read article →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <span class="tag">API</span>
      <h2>Hoppscotch: Lightweight API Testing</h2>
      <p>
        A fast, web-native, and open-source API development suite designed for modern workflows.
      </p>
      <a class="inline-link" href="/blog/hoppscotch-lightweight-api-testing">Read article →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <span class="tag">AI Tools</span>
      <h2>Exploring Antigravity Claude Proxy</h2>
      <p>
        How to use Anthropic's Claude Code CLI for free by proxying requests through Google's GenAI infrastructure—and the risks involved.
      </p>
      <a class="inline-link" href="/blog/antigravity-claude-proxy">Read article →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <span class="tag">OpenClaw</span>
      <h2>What is OpenClaw?</h2>
      <p>
        A practical introduction to OpenClaw: what it is, how it works, and why it matters for people
        who want a self-hosted AI assistant they can actually message from anywhere.
      </p>
      <a class="inline-link" href="/blog/what-is-openclaw">Read article →</a>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
.article-list {
  display: grid;
  gap: 18px;
  padding: 24px 0 56px;
}
.card h2 {
  margin: 14px 0 10px;
}
</style>
